Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:03.45,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(356,313)}『　　　　　　　　　←笨蛋是看不见答案的』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:03.45,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,305)}教师点评
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.45,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(162,210)}——原来着这样打算的，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.45,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(136,165)}但你们两人例外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.45,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(110,143}零分处理。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后过了一个礼拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课程也正式开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对还没熟悉日语的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现代国语到底在上什么完全听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是对于古典文学 更是难解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么久请吉井同学 在这情况下的活用形应该是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  华丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你古文的活用形 答案却回答的京都方言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是令人愉悦到猴年马月的回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在下次上课前请复习学到现在的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到总算从拷问般无聊的课堂解放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛田同学 要去哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 what a sea？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,wa ta shi （我）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原来说了我要回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉没有听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛田同学是从外国回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为说的是外语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于不习惯日语的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能够挺清楚他说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要努力去理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大脑追不上 好像要爆炸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一会还有班会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 现在还不能回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 再等等就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙在笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能说日语就这么有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在说美波中学的时候参加了什么社团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是现在该问的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说回来这家伙的日语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和文法合得上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么大家都不了解我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这么努力了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:01.72,D2,+,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.18,D2,+,0,0,0,,欢迎回来的说 姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说大家都讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.35,D2,+,0,0,0,,学校怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.27,D2,+,0,0,0,,非常有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实不应该来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.19,D2,+,0,0,0,,找到朋友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:17.19,D2,+,0,0,0,,有很多不错的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.69,D2,+,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.11,D2,+,0,0,0,,嗯 日本真是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.53,D2,+,0,0,0,,那真是太好了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍然没能融入班级之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白日语 没法交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有谈话物件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是恶性循环
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因是最初的那一天给人印象很差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天从弄错名字的汉字开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 这应该是保持着错误的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 明久 开物中学出身的家伙们说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上小卖部面包来打篮球 你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个月的伙食费很紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让老夫来参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙什么时候变得这么要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa dobuniru monami！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa dobuniru monami！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊这家伙 说些不明所以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白日语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来莫娜美是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是莫娜美而是美波啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明连我名字都记不住 别套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa dobuniru monoomi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu …
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别向我搭话 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别踢我脚？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.87,D2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,635)}你这家伙到底多欠操啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是man, you are？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是男人啊 那么难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛田是个男的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙连英语都没法沟通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙到底多欠操啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说对你感到不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对着愤怒的女生叫她男的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆子不小啊 明久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的 岛田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是因为岛田童鞋的胸部很小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才认为岛田同学是个男的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不过使用常识来想的疼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不明白日语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不知道为什么只有胸部小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一部分清清楚楚的听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙到底多欠操啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不应该来日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 岛田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是刚认识那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是个非常有趣的家伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Baka
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙说的话 去查查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊是说笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa到底是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是在把我当傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去查查那家伙在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再去戏弄那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到有印象的单词
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底说了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说回来那是日语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我的名字都没有合上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明不是莫娜美是美波啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫娜美？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.20,D2,+,0,0,0,,为什么这样叫我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:36.45,D2,+,0,0,0,,不是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:39.91,D2,+,0,0,0,,那不是莫娜美而是mon amie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.42,Default,+,0,0,0,,法国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TU NE BOUDRAIS DEVENIR MON AMIE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是日语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也不是德语
